            <title>[LU-916] preallocate or pin debug pages to avoid contention with OSS read cache</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-916</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As a sub-task of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-874&quot; title=&quot;Client eviction on lock callback timeout &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-874&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-874&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; we need to be able to reliably collect debug data while the OSS read cache is enabled.  Otherwise, the tage allocations fail too often and drop debug messages while also flooding the console with error messages.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
